/* BEFORE AUTOMATION
* Gamepad 1:
*
* Left joystick X and Y - strafe (drive)
* Right joystick X - turn (drive)
*
* Left Bumper -
* Right Bumper -
*
* Left trigger - retract horizontal slide
* Right trigger - extend horizontal slides
*
* A -
* B -
* Y -
* X -
*
* D-Pad Up-
* D-Pad Down -
* D-Pad Left-
* D-Pad Right -
*
