/* AFTER AUTOMATION
*
* Gamepad 1:
*
* Left joystick X and Y - strafe (drive)
* Right joystick X - turn (drive)
*
* Left Bumper -
* Right Bumper -
*
* Left trigger -
* Right trigger -
*
* A - auto-extend intake, then retract once picked up piece (scoring)
* B - vertical slide extend, then deposit, then retract (scoring)
* Y - slow mode toggle (drive)
* X - reset gyro (drive)
*
* D-Pad Up-
* D-Pad Down -
* D-Pad Left-
* D-Pad Right -
*

